title: Swimming pool! Enjoy balcony, Large 1BR apt, Located in West San Jose
posting_body: ['The Viva Apartments is adjacent to Starbird Park in West San Jose and offers\xa0one and two bedroom apartments with\xa0spacious floor plans, ample storage and cabinet space, and plenty of covered parking.', 'The ideal location is\xa0just minutes from\xa0Cupertino, Campbell, Los Gatos, and has easy\xa0access to major highways such as 280 and 880, making it great for commuters.', '\xa0Enjoy quality dining and shopping at the nearby Westfield Valley Fair shopping mall and Santana Row.', 'This apartment features:', 'Located on 2nd floor', 'Enjoy your balcony', 'Great pool view', 'Plenty of natural light', 'Granite countertops', 'Generous pantry', 'Wood-style flooring throughout', 'Walk-in closet', 'Come Visit us!', 'Viva Apartments', '1118 Starbird Cir', 'San Jose, CA 95117', '<URL>', 'Contact us today to schedule a tour!', 'Call', 'show contact info', 'Photos in ad may not be of actual apartment, however we try our best to use photos similar to the floor plan.', 'related search terms ::: West San Jose, Starbird Park, San Tomas Expy, 280, 880/17, Santana Row, Westfield Valley Fair, Campbell, Los Gatos, Cupertino']
